Use the standard library
This is how to count_distinct_characters of string:
   Remember that seen is ""
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this string's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in string
      When c is not in seen, then:
         Add seen to c
         Increase count
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
